# Carta de formantes
####################

Erase all
Select outer viewport: 0.5, 8, 1, 7
Draw inner box
Axes: 3000, 300, 1500, 200
Text left: "yes", "F1"
Text bottom: "yes", "F2"

Red
select tab_f_a_first
Draw ellipses: "F2", 3000, 300, "F1", 1500, 200, "vocalFonol", 1, 12, "no"
select tab_f_a_second
